e world.\", \"from\": 1318, \"to\": 1405, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1319, \"end\": 1330, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_Bocuse\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paul Bocuse\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_Bocuse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_Bocuse\"}, {\"begin\": 1372, \"end\": 1378, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.6044710249267785, \"rank\": 0.4055628462646571, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nowadays, there are more than 70 countries that start out at the beginning of the process, and end with 24 in the finals.\\\"\", \"from\": 1406, \"to\": 1528, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Arnold was intending to next represent Australia at the 2027 competition, until he swapped years with Paul Golding, head chef at Barn & Co on the Mornington Peninsula.\", \"from\": 1530, \"to\": 1697, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1530, \"end\": 1536, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arnold_Schwarzenegger\", \"score\": 0.9999983865331443, \"rank\": 1.5787608860304276e-06, \"text\": \"Arnold\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arnold_Schwarzenegger\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arnold_Schwarzenegger\"}, {\"begin\": 1569, \"end\": 1578, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9987821657955531, \"rank\": 0.0011311133547238326, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 1632, \"end\": 1644, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_Golding\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paul Golding\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_Golding\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_Golding\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But competing in 2025 also holds personal significance for Arnold as it marks 20 years since his longtime mentor, the late Serge Vieira, won the competition in 2005.\", \"from\": 1699, \"to\": 1864, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1758, \"end\": 1764, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arnold_Schwarzenegger\", \"score\": 0.9999983865331443, \"rank\": 1.5787608860304276e-06, \"text\": \"Arnold\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arnold_Schwarzenegger\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arnold_Schwarzenegger\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Arnold worked with Vieira for seven years at his two-Michelin-starred Restaurant Serge Vieira in France, and he was deeply affected by his death in July last year.\", \"from\": 1865, \"to\": 2028, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1865, \"end\": 1871, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arnold_Schwarzenegger\", \"score\": 0.9999983865331443, \"rank\": 1.5787608860304276e-06, \"text\": \"Arnold\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arnold_Schwarzenegger\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arnold_Schwarzenegger\"}, {\"begin\": 1962, \"end\": 1968, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.976354605963639, \"rank\": 0.024073642573841033, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He was like a second father to me,\\\" Arnold says.\", \"from\": 2030, \"to\": 2079, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2067, \"end\": 2073, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arnold_Schwarzenegger\", \"score\": 0.9999983865331443, \"rank\": 1.5787608860304276e-06, \"text\": \"Arnold\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arnold_Schwarzenegger\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arnold_Schwarzenegger\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And not just from a cooking point of view.\", \"from\": 2080, \"to\": 2123, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We were in each other's lives for seven years, side by side.\", \"from\": 2124, \"to\": 2184, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"His second child and my first child were born one month apart.\", \"from\": 2185, \"to\": 2247, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He was the one who pushed me forward to go into the Bocuse the first time.\", \"from\": 2249, \"to\": 2324, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"[Without] the time I spent with him, I would not be where I am today, professionally or personally.\", \"from\": 2325, \"to\": 2424, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This year's going to be a lot about honouring his memory.\\\"\", \"from\": 2425, \"to\": 2483, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In the Asia Pacific round, Arnold will have 5\\u00bd hours to create two dishes that include mandatory ingredients.\", \"from\": 2485, \"to\": 2594, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2512, \"end\": 2518, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arnold_Schwarzenegger\", \"score\": 0.9999983865331443, \"rank\": 1.5787608860304276e-06, \"text\": \"Arnold\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arnold_Schwarzenegger\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arnold_Schwarzenegger\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The first is presented on a plate, while the second is showcased on a platter before being plated up for the jury.\", \"from\": 2595, \"to\": 2709, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Since last competing in the Bocuse d'Or, Arnold has become a co-owner in three restaurants - Restaurant Dan Arnold, La Cache a Vin and Pneuma - and says he's evolved as a chef.\", \"from\": 2711, \"to\": 2887, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2739, \"end\": 2750, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bocuse_d'Or\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 2.2054863710942184e-13, \"text\": \"Bocuse d'Or\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bocuse_d'Or\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bocuse_d'Or\"}, {\"begin\": 2752, \"end\": 2758, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arnold_Schwarzenegger\", \"score\": 0.9999983865331443, \"rank\": 1.5787608860304276e-06, \"text\": \"Arnold\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arnold_Schwarzenegger\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arnold_Schwarzenegger\"}, {\"begin\": 2819, \"end\": 2825, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arnold_Schwarzenegger\", \"score\": 0.9999983865331443, \"rank\": 1.5787608860304276e-06, \"text\": \"Arnold\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arnold_Schwarzenegger\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arnold_Schwarzenegger\"}, {\"begin\": 2846, \"end\": 2852, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pneuma\", \"score\": 0.999999999998181, \"rank\": 1.9507569881899372e-12, \"text\": \"Pneuma\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pneuma\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pneuma\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In 2017, I was just like a machine running the kitchen non-stop,\\\" he says.\", \"from\": 2889, \"to\": 2964, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I did not have the maturity I have now.\", \"from\": 2965, \"to\": 3005, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have my own idea of how I want to do this.\", \"from\": 3006, \"to\": 3050, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I will take on more ideas from other people around me, but I will not let them make my decisions.\", \"from\": 3051, \"to\": 3148, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's probably the biggest difference.\", \"from\": 3149, \"to\": 3188, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I would not say I am more confident [this time around], but I am excited - really excited to be back on the bandwagon.\\\"\", \"from\": 3190, \"to\": 3310, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Leading up to the competition, Arnold is hosting a series of dinners to help raise funds for the Australian entry.\", \"from\": 3312, \"to\": 3426, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3343, \"end\": 3349, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arnold_Schwarzenegger\", \"score\": 0.9999983865331443, \"rank\": 1.5787608860304276e-06, \"text\": \"Arnold\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arnold_Schwarzenegger\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arnold_Schwarzenegger\"}, {\"begin\": 3409, \"end\": 3419, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9683390190926682, \"rank\": 0.014294692544490334, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have a small budget in Australia and a relatively small number of sponsors,\\\" he says.\", \"from\": 3428, \"to\": 3517, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3455, \"end\": 3464, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9987821657955531, \"rank\": 0.0011311133547238326, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Ideally though, it's about getting people hearing and talking about it as much as possible.\", \"from\": 3518, \"to\": 3610, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's just about sharing the experience with our customers and allowing them to participate in a way.\", \"from\": 3612, \"to\": 3713, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"